## Development Workflow

### Build

```bash
# Build all crates
cargo build --workspace

# Build with all features
cargo build --workspace --all-features

# Release build
cargo build --release
```

### Test

```bash
# All tests
cargo test --workspace

# Specific crate
cargo test -p {{package_name}}

# Specific test
cargo test test_name -- --exact

# With log output
RUST_LOG=debug cargo test -- --nocapture

# Doc tests
cargo test --doc
```

### Code Quality

Run before every commit:

```bash
# Format
cargo fmt --all

# Lint (pedantic, warnings as errors)
cargo clippy --workspace --all-features -- -D warnings -W clippy::pedantic

# Audit dependencies
cargo audit
cargo deny check
```

### Security Scanning

```bash
/vuln-scan           # Vulnerability scan (cargo-audit + cargo-deny)
/memory-audit        # Unsafe code and memory safety audit
/scan-secrets        # Scan for hardcoded credentials
/supply-chain-audit  # Full dependency security review
```

